name: rengineeringjobs
overview:
www.rengineeringjobs.com is owned and operated by R Job Network Ltd one of the worlds’s leading providers of online recruitment solutions to the technical and engineering industries.

R Engineering Jobs was launched in April 2010 and has grown to become one of the world’s largest engineering job boards with over 400,000 members registered and over 15,000 new candidates registering ever single month.

The management team has worked in the online recruitment industry for over 10 years having sold a previous business in 2007 to Jobsite.co.uk one of the world’s leading generic job boards.
